Qore tar Module Release Notes
==============================

Version 1.0.0
-------------
- Initial release
- TarFile class for reading and writing TAR archives
- Support for compression methods: none, gzip, bzip2, xz, zstd, lz4
- Support for TAR formats: ustar, pax, GNU, V7
- TarInputStream and TarOutputStream for streaming operations
- Stream-based I/O (read/write from Qore InputStream/OutputStream)
- In-memory archive operations
- File metadata handling (permissions, ownership, timestamps)
- Support for special file types (symlinks, hardlinks, sparse files, device nodes)
- Archive encryption helper functions (AES-256-CBC)
- Multi-volume archive support (split/join)
- TarDataProvider module with 16 registered actions
- Comprehensive test suite with unit, integration, negative, and corner case tests
